{"tid":1598222,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發］藍絲十一劇本","createTime":"2019-09-27T10:39:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T14:25:33.000Z","uid":173883,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a6b41499fb41dfaf09395f29883fb595c9cb8e9f","tid":1598222,"uid":173883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T10:39:40.000Z","msg":"收到情報，十月一日全港大暴動，暴徒遍地開花地點:<br />\n<br />\n北區：北區運動場<br />\n大埔：天后宮風水廣場<br />\n沙田：新城市<br />\n黃大仙：黃大仙廣場<br />\n九龍城：亞皆老街球場<br />\n深水埗：深水埗運動場<br />\n觀塘：apm<br />\n西貢：單車館<br />\n油尖旺：紅磡體育館外<br />\n葵青：葵涌運動場<br />\n荃灣：沙咀道運動場<br />\n屯門：屯門公園<br />\n元朗：元朗公園<br />\n南區：香港仔中心<br />\n中西區：中山紀念公園<br />\n灣仔：維園<br />\n東區：太古城<br />\n離島：東薈城/梅窩碼頭<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n30年來，第一次，輔警總監要求全港輔警出動，預測當日全港各區將會烽煙四起，正輔警察會聯合奮力抵抗暴徒曱甴 💪🏻<br />\n<br />\n要通知亲朋好友，留在家中，不要上街，以减少警察负担！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>唔知真唔真呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"26d7f19f1c58af687eace4528bd9624d65156e94","tid":1598222,"uid":77717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T10:40:21.000Z","msg":"[update再update] [新增地圖] 黑警狗竇合集<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1594473\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1594473</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4c62160f46080abf127c30349c6374b58a99f26b","tid":1598222,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T10:40:43.000Z","msg":"沒一個是港島，即是話港島見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf916cb30767dacacc3961b91c855cbcb08c561c","tid":1598222,"uid":280452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T10:41:17.000Z","msg":"殘體<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97f7050119cdac7e4eb9e5fdc2704cc89ca73360","tid":1598222,"uid":287433,"like":2,"dislike":0,"sc